Texts.Chs:
^orange;1级^reset;

^orange;加工台^reset;是生产机械零件的地方，并且作为基础工作站为您的许多科学探索奠定基础。你已经学会了用加加工台自己制作还有各种基本项目在工程中使用，。

要制作一张^orange;加工台^reset;，你需要使用你的基础^green;[C]^reset;制作菜单。

Texts.Eng:
^orange;Tier 1^reset;

The ^orange;Machining Table^reset; is the place to produce mechanical components, and will serve as the base workstation for many of your scientific forays. You've learned to create one yourself along with variety of basic items used in engineering.

To craft a ^orange;Machining Table^reset; you'll need to use your basic ^green;[C]rafting^reset; menu.

^orange;Tier 1^reset;

You've learned the basics of resource extraction and can now build rudimentary devices to extract, research and centrifuge materials. 

^cyan;Extractor^reset;

Put almost anything in and it will convert it into something else. Most items are processed in groups of 50. 

^cyan;Centrifuge^reset;

Put any liquid inside and the centrifuge will start working - though the wooden one isn't quite durable enough to handle lava and other volatile stuff. Researched in the ^orange;Power Systems^reset; tree. 

^cyan;Research Computer^reset;

Put an item with a value greater than 0 in one and it will automatically convert it into an amount of research equal to ^green;1% of the item's pixel value^reset;. Learned by pursuing ^orange;Gold Circuitry^reset; research.

Texts.Chs:
^orange;2级^reset;

厄尔吉斯水晶背后的科学原理仍然棱模两可，但有一件事是确定的: 这些水晶掌握着超光速旅行的关键。有了制造你自己FTL驱动器的能力，整个宇宙现在都可以进行探索了。

当以厄尔吉斯水晶为基础的引擎仍处于初级阶段时，只有厄尔吉斯燃料可以为 FTL 旅行提供动力。然而，人们已经发现了如何使用^green;放射性同位素^reset;或^green;生物燃料^reset;等多种物质来驱动引擎。

Texts.Eng:
^orange;Tier 2^reset;

The science behind Erchius Crystals is still very vague, but one thing is known for certain: these crystals hold the key to FTL travel. With the ability to make your own FTL drives, the whole galaxy is now open to exploration.

When Erchius-based drives were still in their infancy, only Erchius fuel could power FTL travel. However, it has since been discovered how to fuel drives with a variety of sources such as ^green;radioactive isotopes^reset; or ^green;biofuel^reset;.

Texts.Chs:
^orange;3级^reset;

随着对计算机技术和物理学的深入了解，你现在可以创建力场，^green;保护你的基地以免遭伤害^reset;，^green;控制重力^reset;，并^green;提供可呼吸的空气^reset;。非常有用！

为了保护某个位置，请在该区域周围的正方形的对角放置两个力场标记，并将它们力接到磁场发生器的输出连接器上。力场扩展器可以用作继电器，以连接超出正常布线范围的力场标记。

Texts.Eng:
^orange;Tier 3^reset;

With a solid understand of computer technology and physics you can now create Force Fields that ^green;protect your base from harm^reset;, ^green;control gravity^reset; and ^green;provide breathable air^reset;. Quite useful!

To protect a location, place two field markers at the opposite corners of a square around the area, and wire them to the field generator's output connector. Field extenders can be used as relays, to connect the field markers beyond the normal wiring range.
